# Windy Chain Intelligence

## Environment Variables
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=5432
DB_NAME=windychain
DB_USERNAME=postgres
DB_PASSWORD=postgres
REDIS_HOST=localhost
REDIS_PORT=6379
